(162, 1, '2014-04-10 17:07:55', '2014-04-10 17:07:55', '<div class="panel panel-default review-box">\r\n				  <div class="panel-body">\r\n					<h3 class="title-img">Why Should You Consider a Corporate Tour?</h3>		 \r\n					<img height="400" src="../wp-content/uploads/2014/04/IMG_4992.jpg" class=" thumbnail">\r\n					\r\nOur Soho tour is the perfect activity to enhance social, corporate or team building events. We work with local businesses and local foodies like us, that are passionate about what they do. In addition to simply tasting foods, \r\nwe try to bring together the people behind the scenes with participants of the tour, so our groups can fully understand their passion for what they do. \r\n\r\nYour group will be provided with an expert Food Guide, that will bring you to some of Soho’s most famous institutions, while, keeping your group entertained as well as informed about food, cultures, and interesting historical points. Your group will get a more unique and personalized \r\nunderstanding of Soho’s International food scene. \r\n\r\nThis is the perfect option for corporate groups that are looking for a more exclusive and customized experience.\r\n					<h4>What’s the Next Step?</h4>	\r\n\r\nWe offer an exploration of Soho’s International foods through 10 different tastings, including Hawaiian, Italian, Mexican, British, French, Chinese, Indian, and New Zealand. However, if you are looking for something in particular, let us know and we can customize your tour.\r\n\r\nFill out the information Corporate Tour Request Form, and let us know how we can help you create the perfect tour to meet your company’s needs.\r\n\r\n<h4>Still have questions?</h4>	\r\n\r\nWe will answer all of your questions by phone or email once we receive the completed Private Tour Request Form.\r\n\r\n					\r\n				  </div>\r\n				</div>\r\n	<div class="panel panel-default review-box">\r\n				  <div class="panel-body">			\r\n				<h3>Here are some pictures from our latest private tours!</h3